HEADWORD: Reillume
<hw>Re`il*lume"</hw> <pr>(r?`?l*l?m")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To
light again; to cause to shine anew; to relume; to reillumine.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Thou must <xex>reillume</xex> its spark.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>J. R.
